    <item>
      <title>如何科学猜拳</title>
      <link>https://yimmyjiyh.com/posts/32de6cd9.html</link>
      <guid>https://yimmyjiyh.com/posts/32de6cd9.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Jan 2021 02:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;📘 摘要：该文主要讲述为什么石头剪刀布的纳什均衡点在(1/3,1/3,1/3)，以及为什么遗憾最小化算法可以逼近纳什均衡。此为组会汇报&lt;a href=&quot;https://yimmyjiyh.com/posts/df773e73.html#more&quot;&gt;上一篇博客内容&lt;/a&gt;时被老师问倒了的两个问题，供大家参考。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>📘 摘要：该文主要讲述为什么石头剪刀布的纳什均衡点在(1/3,1/3,1/3)，以及为什么遗憾最小化算法可以逼近纳什均衡。此为组会汇报<a href="https://yimmyjiyh.com/posts/df773e73.html#more">上一篇博客内容</a>时被老师问倒了的两个问题，供大家参考。</p><a id="more"></a> <hr><p><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_01.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_02.jpg" alt=""></p><h1 id="1-石头剪刀布的纳什均衡"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-石头剪刀布的纳什均衡">¶</a>1 石头剪刀布的纳什均衡</h1><p><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_03.jpg" alt=""></p><h2 id="1-1-石头剪刀布的纳什均衡为什么是在-1-3-1-3-1-3-？"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-1-石头剪刀布的纳什均衡为什么是在-1-3-1-3-1-3-？">¶</a>1.1 石头剪刀布的纳什均衡为什么是在(1/3,1/3,1/3)？</h2><p><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_04.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_05.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_06.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_07.jpg" alt=""></p><h2 id="1-2-遗憾最小化何以逼近纳什均衡？"><a class="header-anchor" href="#1-2-遗憾最小化何以逼近纳什均衡？">¶</a>1.2 遗憾最小化何以逼近纳什均衡？</h2><p><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_08.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_09.jpg" alt=""></p><h1 id="2-CFR算法时间复杂度"><a class="header-anchor" href="#2-CFR算法时间复杂度">¶</a>2 CFR算法时间复杂度</h1><p><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_10.jpg" alt=""><br><img src="/images/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%8C%9C%E6%8B%B3/%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1&amp;%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_11.jpg" alt=""></p><h1 id="参考材料"><a class="header-anchor" href="#参考材料">¶</a>参考材料</h1><p><a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/247435318_741733">[1] 游戏博弈论：洞悉“剪刀-石头-布&quot;背后的纳什均衡</a><br><a href="https://kns.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?dbcode=CMFD&amp;dbname=CMFD201801&amp;filename=1017738456.nh&amp;v=%25mmd2Fg6vLPP94NlqU%25mmd2Fv6QUv0PTl%25mmd2FLayjJTBbQ6PUslWoUJfk6OgdAWtJgLI09YcdSTcA">[2] 基于虚拟遗憾最小化算法的非完备信息机器博弈研究_代佳宁</a><br>[3] Michael Bowling, Neil Burch, Michael Johanson, and Oskari Tammelin. Heads-up Limit Hold’em Poker is Solved. Science, 347(6218): 145-149 (2015)</p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
